title: Cookology CF100 Recirculating Filters, Carbon Charcoal Filters for Cookology Cooker Hoods
features: Cookology CF100 Carbon Charcoal Recirculating Extractor Fan Cooker Hood Filters

This pair of CF100 Filters is required for our Cookology Cooker Hoods when you are not ducting the air in your kitchen outside via a vent for instance if your cooker or hob is against an internal wall.
Carbon filters help absorb smells from cooking before it gets recirculated back into the kitchen.
description: Unbranded CF100 Recirculating Filters This pair of CF100 Filters is required for our Unbranded Range of Cooker Hoods when you are not ducting the air in your kitchen outside via a vent for instance if your cooker or hob is against an internal wall.
